            <p>Transferred from the Office of the Secretary of the
            Commonwealth, 18 May 1959.</p>
            <p>This accession contained materials from three
               offices: the Commission on Economy and Efficiency; the
               Secretary of the Budget; and the Secretary of the
               Commonwealth. The Electoral Board Correspondence is one
               part of this accession.</p>
         </acqinfo>
